message.raw: remove comment on inertial rotation in urdf sdf converter.  It's not the converter's job to worry about usage of model data, plus it's been fixed in [gazebo pull request #379](https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/pull-request/379/handle-inertia-rotation-and-use-full-pose/diff).
